title: HP MSA 2040: Disk Health
agents: hp_msa
catalog: hw/storagehw/hp
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check reports the health states of the disks
 of a HP MSA 2040 storage system. To make it work you have to configure
 the hp_msa datasource program the via WATO.

 If the state of a disk is "OK" then the service state is OK.
 Otherwise the service shows the health status and reason of the disk
 and changes to WARN or CRIT.

item:
 The disk name.

discovery:
 One service is created for each disk.
